dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Alan Ward. May I have your name, please?
Hi Alan, my name is Amanda Russell.
Nice to meet you, Amanda. Can you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is seven eight two four six three.
Thank you, Amanda. Could you also confirm your date of birth to access your account details securely?
Of course, my date of birth is zero six dash one zero dash one nine eight five.
Great, thank you for confirming that, Amanda. Is there anything specific you need help with today?
I need to add a new vehicle to my policy.
I can assist you with that. Please provide me with the make, model, and year of the vehicle you want to add.
Thank you, Alan. The vehicle is a Honda Accord, two zero one eight.
Thank you for the information, Amanda. I will update your policy accordingly. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you for your help, Alan.
You're welcome, Amanda. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
